sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Dashboard Home Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open dashboard home
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Count totals (students, activities, news, resources, staff, upcoming events)
    LW->>DB: Query upcoming calendar events
    LW->>DB: Query latest news and activities
    DB-->>LW: Aggregated counts and recent items
    LW-->>UI: Render stats cards and quick overview

    User->>UI: Refresh page
    UI->>LW: New request
    LW->>DB: Re-query latest totals and items
    DB-->>LW: Updated data
    LW-->>UI: Re-render dashboard widgets
